<h1>Authors and credits</h1>

<p>The Spider would not exist without the direct and indirect contributions of many people. Here we would like to list the people who contributed the most to the program by helping with programming, testing, and providing software we could use to create Spider. We present the Spider development team first, followed by a list of acknowledgements.</p>

<h2>Spider's current creative team</h2>

<p>The people listed below are the creators, testers, and people who directly help work on the current version of Spider and make it available to users.</p><b>Rafał Płatek</b> - idea, project, programming, help for the program, graphics, other<br clear="all"><b>Janusz "januzi" Skudrzyk</b> - testing<br clear="all"><br><h2>Previous collaborators</h2>
